    "description": "Planet V is a monster taming game. What makes this one different? <br><br>You can catch wild monsters out of and in battle. If you can see it, just throw a Capture Cube at it.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146100/extras/4926c23cb02ecd24ceeb0bf37700db15.poster.avif?t=1724182950\" width=564 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146100/extras/4926c23cb02ecd24ceeb0bf37700db15.webm?t=1724182950\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146100/extras/4926c23cb02ecd24ceeb0bf37700db15.mp4?t=1724182950\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Buy and Sell Monsters. Woo Capitalism!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146100/extras/07ac397618a5849389a133df54716e4d.avif?t=1724182950\" width=530 height=412 /></span><br><br>Use items to clear environmental hazards. I'm sure you'll use this responsibly.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146100/extras/048f3af97b237347895fd5266f884fc8.poster.avif?t=1724182950\" width=566 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146100/extras/048f3af97b237347895fd5266f884fc8.webm?t=1724182950\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146100/extras/048f3af97b237347895fd5266f884fc8.mp4?t=1724182950\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Grow affection with Monsters by discovering and appealing to each individual Monsters likes/dislikes.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146100/extras/32961074815b8784ec0ff190af0be711.poster.avif?t=1724182950\" width=596 height=434 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146100/extras/32961074815b8784ec0ff190af0be711.webm?t=1724182950\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146100/extras/32961074815b8784ec0ff190af0be711.mp4?t=1724182950\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Gain a Monster's trust to use some Monster techniques outside of battle. Thankfully not all of them breathe fire..<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146100/extras/54f7ee1cbeee26e8915dec5daf6397f7.poster.avif?t=1724182950\" width=596 height=434 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146100/extras/54f7ee1cbeee26e8915dec5daf6397f7.webm?t=1724182950\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146100/extras/54f7ee1cbeee26e8915dec5daf6397f7.mp4?t=1724182950\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Edit your moves and team quickly. See your progress towards unlocking new moves. Having multiple of the same move is not a good idea.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146100/extras/88ccb85f5299d1d51ecfd43af084baa7.poster.avif?t=1724182950\" width=586 height=488 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146100/extras/88ccb85f5299d1d51ecfd43af084baa7.webm?t=1724182950\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146100/extras/88ccb85f5299d1d51ecfd43af084baa7.mp4?t=1724182950\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Deeper combat featuring Stamina management, Blocking and Dodging.<br>Enemies will remember which techniques were ineffective against your specific Monsters.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146100/extras/7893134f5f23195e3ca872e9f82722eb.avif?t=1724182950\" width=328 height=278 /></span><br><br>Confused? Tooltips can give you more information<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146100/extras/5e7a15b5f1188e255ef19535bcfa34e3.avif?t=1724182950\" width=424 height=160 /></span><br><br>How the same area looks on different save files<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146100/extras/ff142ca02ba33c6adaf45de2d7cfc8ff.avif?t=1724182950\" width=620 height=210 /></span><br><br>Day/Night cycle. What's going on there?<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146100/extras/8cf5af09cea7f512c8e0021f271a56c7.avif?t=1724182950\" width=800 height=478 /></span><br><br>Monsters can change form during battles.<br>Go back and forth between your monster's forms.<br>And more to come, stay tuned!",
